<section id="sn-requirements-version-0.1.0">
  <title>Requirements Version 0.1.0</title>
  <para>
    The goal is to implement enough functionality so that the application is
    useful for playing back audio files. The first version is a marking
    point where some of the basic application design is worked out, which
    includes communication between GUI and backend, data structures for the
    project, serialisation and the audio engine.
  </para>

